\nc<>Today's magical girl activities are over! Thank you everyone
for lending me your power~☆

\nc<>It's true. That tentacle monster, no matter how much you
do, there's no end to it.

\nc<>Rather, because you regularly sweep them away, it might be
fine with just this, meow.
\nc<>Well then, I'll go give the footage to my junior.
\nc<>...Phew~ Alright, I'll go home and sleep.

\nc<>(Of all times, right after the livestream ended...)

(I wonder if everyone will come watch again if I livestream
again?)
\nc<>(...For now, let's just go and see how things are)
